  "epitaph": "It spun the pixels into loops,\nTo capture motion in a byte,\nA vibrant, endless, silent troop,\nThat made the web feel lighter.\nThough stars still burn at forty-nine,\nThe artist\u2019s hand has ceased to move;\nThe code is frozen in its line,\nWith nothing left here to improve.\n\nRest in peace, `gif.js`. Rest in `/dev/null`.",
